             were indicted, the first for <rs id="t17720429-44-off216" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17720429-44-off216" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17720429-44-off216" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a featherbed value 18 s. a feather bolster value 4 s. two feather pillows value 3 s. a quilt value 4 s. and three blankets value 4 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17720429-44-victim398" type="victimName">
                     William
                      Sweetland
                  <interp inst="t17720429-44-victim398" type="surname" value="Sweetland"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17720429-44-victim398" type="given" value="William"></interp>
